node.text:
#ad What I love THE MOST about @googlepixel New Pixel Buds is that the sound quality is AMAZING, they’re super lightweight AND…..how easily it is to match with any of my outfits!😍 Did I mention how affordable they are for being this good of a quality product?! YOU DO NOT want to miss out on getting these!🔥
Listening to music just got better.  #teampixel
